    "truth_anchor": "For Lady Bird, Greta Gerwig was nominated for major awards including Oscar nominations for Best Director and Best Original Screenplay; Lady Bird won the Golden Globe for Best Motion Picture – Musical or Comedy, but Gerwig herself did not personally win that award as an individual recipient.",
